<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>347</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu rén shuō zhōng guó de míng zì jiào kǔ nán, shì yīn tā men méi yǒu xiàng shén yǎng liǎn,
 cháng jīng tòng kǔ, cháng jīng yōu huàn, wǒ men dōu jǔ shǒu qiú shén lái gǎi biàn.
 hěn duō de cūn zhài dōu yǐn yú dà qǐ dà luò de shān, kě wàng qióng kùn de rén men dōu yǎng qǐ pín xuè de liǎn,
 qiú zhǔ ài wēn nuǎn shì shàng měi yī jiān xiǎo wū rén rén jiàn miàn dōu hù dào píng ān.</lyrics>
<title>yǒu rén shuō zhōng guó de míng zì jiào kǔ nán 迦南347</title>
</song>